Navbar with home, movies -> visible at all times

Homepage: trending today, list of movies from API + 'home' in navbar active

After clicking a title, the user is redirected to the movie page + 'movies' in navbar active
Underneath: cast or reviews (one is replacing the other in case of clicking)

Go back button

Movies: searchbar to look for a movie
After clicking 'search', a list with movies accurate to the query appears
